<taxonomicName id="4C704D0CA468FFAEFAF5FB3BFA3DFB6F" authorityName="Razafim. &amp; C. M. Taylor" authorityYear="2017" baseAuthorityName="Razafim. &amp; C. M. Taylor" baseAuthorityYear="2017" box="[1283,1452,1250,1274]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Eumachia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="9" pageNumber="298" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="poggei">
<emphasis id="B904EA9DA468FFAEFAF5FB3BFA3DFB6F" box="[1283,1452,1250,1274]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="298">Eumachia poggei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to be of somewhat unclear identity, but similar to or perhaps not distinct from 
<taxonomicName id="4C704D0CA468FFAEFC2BFAFBFBD7FAAC" box="[989,1094,1314,1338]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Margaritopsis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="9" pageNumber="298" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oddonii">
<emphasis id="B904EA9DA468FFAEFC2BFAFBFBD7FAAC" box="[989,1094,1314,1338]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="298">E. oddonii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
